data.description: This stunning townhome has incredible space and privacy. With an open concept feel, the main level is situated perfectly. Enjoy a cozy night in with the fireplace , or entertain on the deck. The upper level boasts 4 bedrooms, 2 full baths, and the laundry room. The privacy of a primary suite with full bathroom and walk through closet sets the space perfectly. The lower is ready to be finished for added living space. The Forest Lake High School and middle school are within walking distance!
